SMART online chat groups,
<a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20161103231107/http://smartrecovery.infopop.cc/paraentry.php" target="newwin45">
http://smartrecovery.infopop.cc/paraentry.php</a>, and
<li>
SMART message boards,
<a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20161103231107/http://smartrecovery.infopop.cc/eve/ubb.x" target="newwin46">
http://smartrecovery.infopop.cc/eve/ubb.x</a>
</ul>

<p><li>
WFS (Women For Sobriety) also has online chat groups:<br>
<a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20161103231107/http://www.womenforsobriety.org/news_conferences/chat.html" target="newwin47">
