<img src="https://www.orange-papers.info/P20090507_671-Carmen_under_wing.png" border="0" width="800" height="600" alt="Canada Goose gosling under mother's wing"><br>
Carmen under her new mother's wing<br>
</center>

<p>
Here, Carmen is determined to stay right where she is, even though the mother has gotten
up on her feet and is walking around. Carmen has been so hungry for a real goose mother's
attentions that she refuses to give it up now. She won't budge.
</font></font></td></tr></table></center>

<p>
<center><table width="840" border="0" cellpadding="20" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
<font size="4" base="4" face="Times,Roman"><font color="blue">
