more A.A. double-talk &#8212; just another standard
<a href="orange-bait-switch.html#suggested" target="newwin04">bait-and-switch trick</a>.
&quot;The Program&quot; is most assuredly mandated when someone has to get
a &quot;progress&quot; statement signed by a sponsor to please a parole officer or treatment center
&quot;counselor&quot;.
